Starting in 1939, millions of children were sent away from British cities,

00:00:37.216 --> 00:00:42.136
in anticipation that the country would be bombed by Hitler’s Nazi forces.

00:00:42.896 --> 00:00:47.776
Lives were thrown into chaos and confusion by this massive wartime

00:00:47.786 --> 00:00:52.386
mission to safeguard the future of the country - a mission that would have

